    h1 Input / Form Elements Vue Components
    ul.docs-index
    p Form elements allow you to create flexible and beautiful Form layout. Form elements are just well known <a href="../docs/list-view.html">List View</a> (<b><a href="list-view.html">List</a> and <a href="list-item.html">List Item</a> Vue components</b>) but with few additional components.
    p Check out Framework7's <a href="../docs/inputs.html">Inputs / Form Elements</a> for their appearance.

    h2 Input Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li <code><b>f7-list-input</b></code> - list item input element
      li <code><b>f7-input</b></code> - input element

