    h2 Input Slots
    p <code>&lt;f7-list-input&gt;</code> has additional slots for custom elements:
    ul
      li <code><b>default</b></code> - in case of <code>type="select"</code> or <code>type="textarea"</code> - element will be placed inside of <code>select</code> or <code>textarea</code> tags.
      li <code><b>info</b></code> - element will be inserted into container with info message
      li <code><b>error-message</b></code> - element will be inserted into container with error message
      li <code><b>label</b></code> - element will be inserted into container with input's label
      li <code><b>input</b></code> - element will be inserted instead of input element (<code>input</code> prop must be also set to <code>false</code>)

      li <code><b>root-start</b></code> - element will be inserted in the beginning of <code>&lt;li&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>root</b></code> / <code><b>root-end</b></code> - element will be inserted in the end of <code>&lt;li&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>content-start</b></code> - element will be inserted in the beginning of <code>&lt;div class="item-content"&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>content</b></code> / <code><b>content-end</b></code> - element will be inserted in the end of <code>&lt;div class="item-content"&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>inner-start</b></code> - element will be inserted in the beginning of <code>&lt;div class="item-inner"&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>inner</b></code> / <code><b>inner-end</b></code> - element will be inserted in the end of <code>&lt;div class="item-inner"&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>media</b></code> - element will be inserted inside of <code>&lt;div class="item-media"&gt;</code> element

    h2 Input v-model
    p <code>v-model</code> <b>is not supported</b> on <code>f7-list-input</code> / <code>f7-input</code> vue components. Instead, just use the combination of <code>value</code> property and <code>@input</code> event:
    :code(lang="html")
          <template>
            ...
            <f7-list-input
              label="Name"
              type="text"
              :value="name"
              @input="name = $event.target.value"
              placeholder="Your name"
              clear-button
            ></f7-list-input>
            ...
          </template>
          <script>
            export default {
              data() {
                name: '',
              },
              ...
            };
          </script>
